 effort nor the failure tires. The waste remains, the waste remains and kills.', 68879, 0), (432627, 'The will to persevere is often the difference between failure and success.', 32896, 0), (432628, 'In the different voice of women lies the truth of an ethic of care, the tie between relationship and responsibility, and the origins of aggression in the failure of connection.', 18646, 0), (432629, 'It is a changing world because of the newcomers who keep arriving and who leave us behind. Trying to keep pace with them is doomed to inglorious failure, especially as the pace has quickened so much.', 13699, 0), (432630, 'My story as an artist has been about trial and error. It''s been about artist development, character building, struggle, happiness and failure, family, and music.', 68880, 0), (432631, 'The wisest of the wise may err.', 1882, 0), (432632, 'Success is never final, but failure can be.', 68881, 0), (432633, 'It is not a disgrace to fail. Failing is one of the greatest arts in the world.', 66718, 0), (432634, 'Failure sometimes enlarges the spirit. You have to fall back upon humanity and God.', 37070, 0), (432635, 'The person interested in success has to learn to view failure as a healthy, inevitable part of the process of getting to the top.', 5478, 0), (432636, 'Never walk away from failure. On the contrary, study it carefully and imaginatively for its hidden assets.', 14083, 0), (432637, 'There are some defeats more triumphant than victories.', 663, 0), (432638, 'We may be personally defeated, but our principles never!', 55740, 0), (432639, 'Before you can win a game, you have to not lose it.', 62232, 0), (432640, 'You always pass failure on your way to success.', 64620, 0), (432641, 'Failure is a word that I simply don''t accept.', 68178, 0), (432642, 'The way most people fail is in not keeping up the heart.', 21592, 0), (432643, 'Failure has been my best friend as a writer. It tests you, to see if you have what it takes to see it through.', 38, 0), (432644, 'Optimism is a kind of heart stimulant - the digitalis of failure.', 4, 0), (432645, 'Never fret for an only son, the idea of failure will never occur to him.', 266, 0), (432646, 'It''s how you deal with failure that determines how you achieve success.', 28270, 0), (432647, 'To begin to think with purpose, is to enter the ranks of those strong ones who only recognize failure as one of the pathways to attainment.', 2970, 0), (432648, 'Failure too is a form of death.', 429, 0), (432649, 'Failure in the theater is more dramatic and uglier than any other form of writing. It costs so much, you feel so guilty.', 1991, 0), (432650, 'The key to accepting responsibility for your life is to accept the fact that your choices, every one of them, are leading you inexorably to either success or failure, however you define those terms.', 68736, 0);
