m its hiding place.', 751, 0), (433638, 'If love is the treasure, laughter is the key.', 65730, 0), (433639, 'You know, maybe I was just born in the wrong time, but I love all things romantic. Puffy understands that. For my last birthday, he covered my hotel room floor with rose petals and had flowers and candles all over the room.', 24514, 0), (433640, 'There is more pleasure in loving than in being beloved.', 1348, 0), (433641, 'Love means not ever having to say you''re sorry.', 208, 0), (433642, 'Love cures people - both the ones who give it and the ones who receive it.', 924, 0), (433643, 'Your self-esteem won''t come from body parts. You need to step away from the mirror every once in a while, and look for another reflection, like the one in the eyes of the people who love you and admire you.', 36959, 0), (433644, 'I''m not done with love, but I refuse to settle. I am a hopeless romantic. And I won''t stop till I get it right.', 69081, 0), (433645, 'All married couples should learn the art of battle as they should learn the art of making love. Good battle is objective and honest - never vicious or cruel. Good battle is healthy and constructive, and brings to a marriage the principles of equal partnership.', 3199, 0), (433646, 'There are other things that I could do, but there''s really nothing that I love as much as horse racing.', 69082, 0), (433647, 'When you are older you will understand how precious little things, seemingly of no value in themselves, can be loved and prized above all price when they convey the love and thoughtfulness of a good heart.', 62267, 0), (433648, 'I was born with an enormous need for affection, and a terrible need to give it.', 999, 0), (433649, 'I''m not saying that love always takes you to heaven. Your life can become a nightmare. But that said, it is worth taking the risk.', 34, 0), (433650, 'Love is the only sane and satisfactory answer to the problem of human existence.', 190, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (433651, 'I think people who are creative are the luckiest people on earth. I know that there are no shortcuts, but you must keep your faith in something Greater than You, and keep doing what you love. Do what you love, and you will find the way to get it out to the world.', 7212, 0), (433652, 'Listen to the inner light; it will guide you. Listen to inner peace; it will feed you. Listen to inner love; it will transform you, it will divinise you, it will immortalise you.', 4786, 0), (433653, '''Tis love that makes the world go round, my baby.', 96, 0), (433654, 'Waking up every day and loving someone who may or may not love us back, whose safety we can''t ensure, who may stay in our lives or may leave without a moment''s notice, who may be loyal to the day they die or betray us tomorrow - that''s vulnerability.', 247, 0), (433655, 'Being in love with somebody is a wonderful feeling.', 60068, 0), (433656, 'Everybody has fallen down or been disappointed in love. Where you truly shine is when you get back up. Use it as a learning experience and believe in all of the possibilities.', 794, 0), (433657, 'If you can learn to love yourself and all the flaws, you can love other people so much better. And that makes you so happy.', 3494, 0), (433658, 'At sunrise everything is luminous but not clear. It is those we live with and love and should know who elude us. You can love completely without complete understanding.', 1625, 0), (433659, 'I just love working hard. I love being part of a team I love working toward a common goal. ', 66949, 0), (433660, 'I love holidays. It''s such a wonderful time for the whole family to be together and not have to worry about schedules and that kind of thing.', 69083, 0), (433661, 'No woman ever hates a man for being in love with her, but many a woman hate a man for being a friend to her.', 3348, 0), (433662, 'Breakfast is a big deal. I love it.', 69084, 0), (433663, 'We need 4 hugs a day for survival. We need 8 hugs a day for maintenance. We need 12 hugs a day for growth.', 813, 0), (433664, 'I have a very strong feeling that the opposite of love is not hate - it''s apathy. It''s not giving a damn.', 406, 0), (433665, 'The more people love you, the more there''s going to be people that hate you.', 66658, 0), (433666, 'Talent alone gets you nowhere. You really have to have the grit, and you gotta have a love for people.', 69085, 0), (433667, 'In the end, the love you take is equal to the love you make.', 67, 0), (433668, 'Love is the only gold.', 63203, 0), (433669, 'I am happier when I love than when I am loved. I adore my husband, my son, my grandchildren, my mother, my dog, and frankly, I don''t know if they even like me. But who cares? Loving them is my joy.', 441, 0), (433670, 'The way to know life is to love many things.', 89, 0), (433671, 'You don''t walk away if you love someone. You help the person.', 66567, 0), (433672, 'Some think love can be measured by the amount of butterflies in their tummy. Others think love can be measured in bunches of flowers, or by using the words ''for ever.'' But love can only truly be measured by actions. It can be a small thing, such as peeling an orange for a person you love because you know they don''t like doing it.', 372, 0), (433673, 'I have a personal ambition to live my life honestly and honor the true love that I''ve had and also the people I''ve had around me. I want to stay hopeful, even though I get scared about why we''re even alive at all.', 659, 0), (433674, 'Love at first sight is easy to understand it''s when two people have been looking at each other for a lifetime that it becomes a miracle. ', 1260, 0), (433675, 'I work really hard at trying to see the big picture and not getting stuck in ego. I believe we''re all put on this planet for a purpose, and we all have a different purpose... When you connect with that love and that compassion, that''s when everything unfolds.', 1217, 0), (433676,