res life.', 59119, 0), (433938, 'Love is the child of illusion and the parent of disillusion.', 1504, 0), (433939, 'All love is vanquished by a succeeding love.', 782, 0), (433940, 'Love is a sacred reserve of energy it is like the blood of spiritual evolution. ', 531, 0), (433941, 'You don''t have to go looking for love when it''s where you come from.', 3350, 0), (433942, 'There''s no bad consequence to loving fully, with all your heart. You always gain by giving love.', 61441, 0), (433943, 'Stolen kisses are always sweetest.', 840, 0), (433944, 'Oh, love will make a dog howl in rhyme.', 61515, 0), (433945, 'Great thoughts come from the heart.', 64242, 0), (433946, 'True love is quiescent, except in the nascent moments of true humility.', 24882, 0), (433947, 'You don''t want to love - your eternal and abnormal craving is to be loved. You aren''t positive, you''re negative. You absorb, absorb, as if you must fill yourself up with love, because you''ve got a shortage somewhere.', 178, 0), (433948, 'The spring of love becomes hidden and soon filled up.', 69005, 0), (433949, 'The inner reality of love can be recognized only by love.', 1758, 0), (433950, 'I was adored once too.', 13, 0);
